                    Is your Kalamazoo home's roof showing signs of wear and tear? Don't wait until it's too late! Learn the five critical warning signs that indicate your roof needs immediate professional attention. From water stains to sagging roof decks, these red flags could mean the difference between a simple repair and a complete roof replacement. Discover what local roofing experts say about protecting your home from Michigan's challenging weather conditions.
